data.name: rbac_desc
data.value: Webmin's RBAC integration provides a way for user module and ACL permissions to be determined from an RBAC (Role Based Access Control) database, rather than Webmin's own configuration files. Once RBAC support is enabled, any user for whom the RBAC controls all modules and ACLs option is selected will have his capabilities determined by RBAC rather than Webmin's own access control settings.
